    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>外婆的老屋等待着你……</strong></h2>《COLINA: Legacy》是一款包含解谜元素的独立恐怖游戏。亚历克斯假期拜访外婆老屋，却成了一次恐怖之旅。扮演亚历克斯，克服重重艰难，弄清楚到底发生了什么。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/b37a7b4eae137b65fb51437e526ed501.poster.avif?t=1630882699\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/b37a7b4eae137b65fb51437e526ed501.webm?t=1630882699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/b37a7b4eae137b65fb51437e526ed501.mp4?t=1630882699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>年轻的亚历克斯醒来发现自己孤身一人，种种恐怖之事挑战着他的心智。他必须逃出生天，巧用自己的智慧克服面前的怖骇，否则要失去的不只是神志而已。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>悸怖密室逃脱——《COLINA: Legacy》的游戏设计从密室逃脱中汲取灵感。在探索外婆老屋的过程中，亚历克斯会面对极具挑战性的谜题，不过旅途中等待着他的，不仅是谜题而已……</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/53347241b2a759e5bc70a56eaae373ab.poster.avif?t=1630882699\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/53347241b2a759e5bc70a56eaae373ab.webm?t=1630882699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/53347241b2a759e5bc70a56eaae373ab.mp4?t=1630882699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>回归老派生存恐怖游戏——从第三人称视角到以手电筒为唯一的武器，《COLINA: Legacy》在向过去经典生存恐怖游戏致敬的同时，也是在此类游戏中为自己争得一席之地。</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>惊艳的视效和音效——虽然《COLINA: Legacy》仅由一个非常小的团队开发，但游戏的视觉效果和音效毫不逊于更大型的游戏。《COLINA: Legacy》的魅力只有亲身经历才可体会！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/42ced2faae9cbacca6360a1da0a61d9b.poster.avif?t=1630882699\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/42ced2faae9cbacca6360a1da0a61d9b.webm?t=1630882699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/371650/extras/42ced2faae9cbacca6360a1da0a61d9b.mp4?t=1630882699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
